Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:14.34,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:22.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:46.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:53.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:09.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.69,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:25.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:33.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:14.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上这一带视野最美的那颗树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:22.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子笑了 笑得天真无邪 她看到了梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:46.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,定定地盯着空中畅游的鱼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:53.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小镇每个角落里渐渐褪色的日子浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,拉钩上吊百年不变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,即使分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:09.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,等待约定实现的心情也寄托在这颗树上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一遍一遍地重复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都止不住泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来又继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:25.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是要印证这一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:33.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,山间回音响不绝 你说是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么就逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要骂我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为肯定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定要什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是又干什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这池塘里面没有生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很寂寥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以去抓点什么回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很喜欢干这种事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没那个心情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你零用钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 会给我多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一千円就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我更喜欢谕吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.44,Default,NTP,405,0,0,,{\fs36}(万元大钞)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一千円都不会给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是五百円
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我叫大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把手表借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得在门禁时间之前回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:39.50,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H51D262&\pos(1288.5,885)}大\N家\N一\N起\N去\N赏\N月\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一届欢乐钓鱼大会要在这个池塘开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木实姐也被叫来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是怎么了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海突然说要去钓鱼赚零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说我坏话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起钓鱼更有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没试过这样的感觉了 不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木实姐喜欢钓鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算很着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前有时也会和小枫和日影一起去钓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 在钓什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要钓碉堡的鲷鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,120,0,0,,{\fs48}mede-tai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,420,0,0,,{\fs48}tai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是个池塘 鲷鱼是钓不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有鲷鱼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想钓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱有时好没有常识呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不过换成抓贝壳的话 就成了大眼睛的意思了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0,540,0,,{\fs48}kai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,600,0,0,,{\fs48}me-dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,570,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H814CF7&\pos(243,156)}me de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,570,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H1F82FD&\pos(687,165)}ka i
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,570,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H339A3D&\pos(495,666)}大 眼 睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拼成这种意思有卵用？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有鱼上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎怎怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点拉上来的话就要逃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉回池塘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉地上的话很可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼到哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那条也不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了 完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们几个完全抓不住时机呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 我捡到一大堆贝壳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏也快点钓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个池塘没有大鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用面包可能会比路亚假饵更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假饵是人造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼为什么会来吃人造的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为形状很像真的食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有的品种是带气味的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼大概会觉得很美味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐咬好闻的橡皮擦是同样的道理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的班主任都一把年纪了还在干这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏没咬呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连小夏也咬橡皮擦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏钓到什么了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是这个池塘的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在坐无影凳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是大家伙 钓到大家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 去叫人来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有水桶可能会不够大装不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要去另外准备个容器
